# Telegram String Session Generator Bot

A production-ready Telegram bot for generating Pyrogram string sessions securely.

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 Generate Pyrogram string sessions securely
- 📱 Support for phone number, OTP, and 2FA
- 🛡️ Rate limiting and session timeout protection
- 👥 Admin commands (stats, broadcast, users)
- 🔒 No storage of sensitive data
- 📊 Basic analytics and logging
- 🌐 Flask health check for deployment
- 🚀 One-click deployment on Render

## 📋 Prerequisites

- Python 3.11+
- Telegram Bot Token (from @BotFather)
- Telegram API ID and Hash (from https://my.telegram.org)

